# Application Types
<kos/application/type/infrastructure> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "Infrastructure"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type> .
<kos/application/type/business> a skos:Concept ; skos:prefLabel "Business Application"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type> .
