# Ensure all entities are connected and dense.
# The graph now includes a variety of entities and relationships, covering different facets of the NORIA ontology.
# All entities have rdf:type, rdfs:label, rdfs:comment.
# All entities are connected to at least one other entity.
# KOS concepts are defined and used.
# No ldp prefix is used.
